{"tid":1372210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首辦拒回覆張建宗道歉是否獲林鄭首肯","createTime":"2019-07-27T11:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T12:29:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc7150cec1c5a1ae9598fe9413d31fb9ed38dbb","tid":1372210,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"警務處人事部昨日透過內部信息向警隊指，表示警務處長事前不知悉張建宗道歉內容，將會陪同四個職方協會約見張建宗。《蘋果》昨晚亦向特首辦查詢，張建宗和警務處就元朗襲擊事件的立場不一，究竟政府立場為何？張建宗的言論是否代表整個政府立場？張建宗發佈有關「道歉」內容前，特首辦或特首是否知悉或准許？特首辦至今未有回覆。 <br />\n<br />\n政府昨晚以消息人士為事件消毒，根據港台和明報昨日今日報道，政府消息人士昨晚為事件解畫降溫，稱張建宗的「道歉論」是針對政府在處理《逃犯條例》修例手法的不足致歉，更指張建宗「絕對支持警隊工作及高度表揚警隊人員努力」。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190727/59869404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59869404&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=91561031\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59869404&h=40825ce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190727/59869404</a>"},{"pid":"0107436f001740f690a674680b404e2a163e4147","tid":1372210,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9d5d2edfc069e198aed6e1687bf9b3792f5f43","tid":1372210,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}